content: kesar: Merged three significant PRs this month, including a package.json update (#2301, +5466/-1508 lines), a major refactoring that replaced AgentRuntime with an interface (#2388, +151006/-266698 lines), and adding Fraxtal chain to EVM (#1954). Made substantial code changes across 1560 files (+77055/-43604 lines) in 8 commits, with 75% of changes in code files and 25% in configuration files. Activity was sporadic, concentrated on just 4 days this month, with PRs taking an average of 312 hours to merge.
